::GoldenEye::

She flew off and headed towards the Pred ship.  She flew towards the 
Pred ship.  She came in close enough so the scanners would pick her 
up, but just out of autogun range.  She waited until she was sure 
they had seen her.  She didn't want to just walk in unannounced.
